  "sections": {
    "Description": "The Alpha Beetle charges forward in a line, dealing 3 damage and pushing the first target it hits.",
    "Strategy": "Much like the standardBeetlebut with more health and damage, the Alpha Beetle charges until it runs into an obstacle, doing damage to its target. This ability can cause the Alpha Beetle to dash itself into a body of water, a chasm, an A.C.I.D. pool, or lava.\nAlternatively, if the Alpha Beetle is first in the attack order, try to displace them so that they target another enemy; since they damageANDpush their target, look for opportunities where they can provide bump damage, push grounded enemies into water, or push another enemy away from a building."
  },
  "full_text": "Alpha Beetle\nDetails\nHealth\n5\nMove\n2\nSystems\nSharpened Pincers\n(\nEnemy\n)\nEffect\nCharge forward to deal 3 damage and push the target.\nAlpha Beetle\nis one of the Alpha\nVek\nfrom\nInto The Breach\n.\nDescription\n[\n]\nThe Alpha Beetle charges forward in a line, dealing 3 damage and pushing the first target it hits.\nStrategy\n[\n]\nMuch like the standard\nBeetle\nbut with more health and damage, the Alpha Beetle charges until it runs into an obstacle, doing damage to its target. This ability can cause the Alpha Beetle to dash itself into a body of water, a chasm, an A.C.I.D. pool, or lava.\nAlternatively, if the Alpha Beetle is first in the attack order, try to displace them so that they target another enemy; since they damage\nAND\npush their target, look for opportunities where they can provide bump damage, push grounded enemies into water, or push another enemy away from a building.\nv\n·\nd\n·\ne\nVek\nVek\nBeetle\n•\nBlobber\n•\nBurrower\n•\nCentipede\n•\nCrab\n•\nDigger\n•\nFirefly\n•\nHornet\n•\nLeaper\n•\nScarab\n•\nScorpion\n•\nSpider\n•\nVolatile Vek\nVek (Advanced Edition)\nBouncer\n•\nGastropod\n•\nMosquito\n•\nMoth\n•\nPlasmodia\n•\nStarfish\n•\nTumblebug\nAlpha Vek\nAlpha Beetle\n•\nAlpha Blobber\n•\nAlpha Burrower\n•\nAlpha Centipede\n•\nAlpha Crab\n•\nAlpha Digger\n•\nAlpha Firefly\n•\nAlpha Hornet\n•\nAlpha Leaper\n•\nAlpha Scarab\n•\nAlpha Scorpion\n•\nAlpha Spider\nAlpha Vek (Advanced Edition)\nAlpha Bouncer\n•\nAlpha Gastropod\n•\nAlpha Mosquito\n•\nAlpha Moth\n•\nAlpha Plasmodia\n•\nAlpha Starfish\n•\nAlpha Tumblebug\nVek Psions\nBlast Psion\n•\nBlood Psion\n•\nShell Psion\n•\nSoldier Psion\nVek Psions (Advanced Edition)\nArachnid Psion\n•\nRaging Psion\n•\nSmoldering Psion\nVek Minions\nBlob\n•\nAlpha Blob\n•\nSpiderling Egg\n•\nSpiderling\n•\nAlpha Spiderling\nVek Minions (Advanced Edition)\nSpore\n•\nAlpha Spore\n•\nVicious Spore\n•\nBlob Leader\nVek Leaders\nBeetle Leader\n•\nFirefly Leader\n•\nHornet Leader\n•\nLarge Goo\n(\nMedium Goo\n) (\nSmall Goo\n) •\nPsion Abomination\n•\nScorpion Leader\n•\nSpider Leader\nVek Leaders (Advanced Edition)\nBlobber Leader\n•\nBouncer Leader\n•\nCentipede Leader\n•\nCrab Leader\n•\nGastropod Leader\n•\nMosquito Leader\n•\nPlasmodia Leader\n•\nScarab Leader\n•\nStarfish Leader\n•\nTumblebug Leader"
